{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-72-counting-fractions","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","demoType":null,"title":"Zoezi la 72: Kuhesabu sehemu","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Razmotrimo razlomak $\\frac{n}{d}$, gde su <code>n</code> i <code>d</code> pozitivni celi brojevi. Ako je <code>n</code> &#x3C; <code>d</code> i najveći zajednički delilac, ${HCF}(n, d) = 1$, tada se on naziva pravilno skraćenim razlomkom.</p>\n<p>Ako navedemo skup tačnih elemenata pojednostavljen za <code>d</code> ≤ 8 u rastućem redosledu veličine, dobijamo:</p>\n<p>$$\\frac{1}{8}, \\frac{1}{7}, \\frac{1}{6}, \\frac{1}{5}, \\frac{1}{4}, \\frac{2}{7}, \\frac{1}{3}, \\frac{3}{8}, \\frac{2}{5}, \\frac{3}{7}, \\frac{1}{2}, \\frac{4}{7}, \\frac{3}{5}, \\frac{5}{8}, \\frac{2}{3}, \\frac{5}{7}, \\frac{3}{4}, \\frac{4}{5}, \\frac{5}{6}, \\frac{6}{7}, \\frac{7}{8}$$</p>\n<p>Izgleda da postoje elementi <code>21</code> u ovom skupu.</p>\n<p>Koliko će elemenata biti u skupu pravilno skraćenih razlomaka za <code>d</code> ≤ <code>limit</code>?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3b41000cf542c50fec7","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302185,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-72-counting-fractions"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function countingFractions(limit) {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\ncountingFractions(8);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>countingFractions(8)</code> treba da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof countingFractions(8) === 'number');"},{"text":"<p><code>countingFractions(8)</code> treba da vrati <code>21</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(countingFractions(8), 21);"},{"text":"<p><code>countingFractions(20000)</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>121590395</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(countingFractions(20000), 121590395);"},{"text":"<p><code>countingFractions(500000)</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>75991039675</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(countingFractions(500000), 75991039675);"},{"text":"<p><code>countingFractions(1000000)</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>303963552391</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(countingFractions(1000000), 303963552391);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-1-to-100","dashedName":"problem-72-counting-fractions","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-73-counting-fractions-in-a-range","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-71-ordered-fractions","id":"5900f3b41000cf542c50fec7","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function arrangedProbability(limit) {\n  // Based on https://www.mathblog.dk/project-euler-100-blue-discs-two-blue/\n  let blue = 15;\n  let discs = 21;\n\n  while (discs < limit) {\n    const nextBlue = 3 * blue + 2 * discs - 2;\n    const nextDiscs = 4 * blue + 3 * discs - 3;\n\n    blue = nextBlue;\n    discs = nextDiscs;\n  }\n  return blue;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-72-counting-f